Simple chessboard in opengl in C

- compile: make
- run: ./chessboard

Move around the chessboard using the keys:

             .---- forward
            w 
 left --- a s d --- right
            '
             `---- backward

Highlight cells:
             .---- forward
            t 
 left --- f g h --- right
            '
             `---- backward

Tested on MacOSX 10.6.8
